data.description: Gorgeous brick front traditional home just minutes from historic Kennesaw. Fresh neutral paint throughout and lots of natural light. Situated on an expansive 1.68 acre lot with a creek, this home offers great living space, a partially finished basement and an HOA optional neighborhood. Begin each day with fresh eggs from the chicken coop or plant a garden in this flat and private backyard. Welcome to the country...right in the middle of it all. Highly rated Allatoona High School district.
